#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.memory_usage.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.memory\\_usage"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:1 of
msgid "Return the memory usage of each column in bytes."
msgstr "返回每个列的内存使用量（以字节为单位）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:3 of
msgid ""
"The memory usage can optionally include the contribution of the index and"
" elements of `object` dtype."
msgstr "内存使用量可以选择性地包括索引和 `object` 类型元素的贡献。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:6 of
msgid ""
"This value is displayed in `DataFrame.info` by default. This can be "
"suppressed by setting ``pandas.options.display.memory_usage`` to False."
msgstr ""
"此值默认显示在 `DataFrame.info` 中。可以通过将 ``pandas.options.display."
"memory_usage`` 设置为 False 来抑制显示。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:9 of
msgid ""
"Specifies whether to include the memory usage of the DataFrame's index in"
" returned Series. If ``index=True``, the memory usage of the index is the"
" first item in the output."
msgstr ""
"指定是否在返回的 Series 中包含 DataFrame 索引的内存使用量。如果 ``index="
"True``，则索引的内存使用量是输出中的第一项。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:13 of
msgid ""
"If True, introspect the data deeply by interrogating `object` dtypes for "
"system-level memory consumption, and include it in the returned values."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则通过深入检查 `object` 类型来获取系统级内存消耗，并将其包含"
"在返回值中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:18 of
msgid ""
"A Series whose index is the original column names and whose values is the"
" memory usage of each column in bytes."
msgstr "一个 Series，其索引为原始列名，值为每列的内存使用量（以字节为单位）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`numpy.ndarray.nbytes`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:25 of
msgid "Total bytes consumed by the elements of an ndarray."
msgstr "ndarray 元素消耗的总字节数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.memory_usage`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:28 of
msgid "Bytes consumed by a Series."
msgstr "Series 消耗的字节数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Categorical`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:31 of
msgid "Memory-efficient array for string values with many repeated values."
msgstr "用于具有许多重复值的字符串的内存高效数组。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.info`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:34 of
msgid "Concise summary of a DataFrame."
msgstr "DataFrame 的简明摘要。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:37 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:69 of
msgid "The memory footprint of `object` dtype columns is ignored by default:"
msgstr "默认情况下，`object` 类型列的内存占用会被忽略："

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.memory_usage.df_memory_usage:80 of
msgid ""
"Use a Categorical for efficient storage of an object-dtype column with "
"many repeated values."
msgstr "使用 Categorical 来高效存储具有许多重复值的 object 类型列。"

